OL,3,CBlast Furnace 5 winds down with steam
OL,4,Cand loud noises expected in Port Talbot
OL,6,FOne of Port Talbot's blast furnaces is
OL,7,Fexpected to produce its final iron
OL,8,Ftoday as Tata Steel presses ahead with
OL,9,Fplans to decarbonise the steelworks.
OL,11,FPeople living nearby have been warned
OL,12,Fto expect plumes of steam and
OL,13,Fwhooshing noises from Blast Furnace 5
OL,14,Fas the winding down process is carried
OL,15,Fout.
OL,17,FThe second, Blast Furnace 4, is due to
OL,18,Fshut at the end of September. The
OL,19,FMorfa Coke Ovens were decommissioned
OL,20,Fin March after concerns about the
OL,21,Fdeteriorating conditions.
