OL,6,FThe steel giant has said the
OL,7,Frestructuring proposals are necessary
OL,8,Fto stem financial losses of up to #1
OL,9,Fmillion a day.
OL,11,FIt is expected that around 1900 people
OL,12,Fwill lose their jobs at the site in
OL,13,FPort Talbot, with around 2500 job
OL,14,Flosses in total across the UK over the
OL,15,Fnext 12 months, followed by another
OL,16,F300 in the next three years.
OL,18,FTata Steel says it is investing #1.25
OL,19,Fbillion and is committed to building
OL,20,Fan electric arc furnace as part of a
OL,21,Ftransition to low-CO2 steelmaking.
