OL,6,FConsultations between the unions and
OL,7,Fthe steel company are ongoing.
OL,9,FThe operations to close Blast Furnace
OL,10,F5 were initiated in July.
OL,12,FThe winding down process means turning
OL,13,Fthe blast furnace off which involves
OL,14,Fseveral steps.
OL,16,FThis week the workers changed the
OL,17,Fburden - the raw materials put in the
OL,18,Ftop of the furnace - reducing the
OL,19,Famount of coal put into the furnace.
