OL,3,CBlast Furnace 5 winds down with steam
OL,4,Cand loud noises expected in Port Talbot
OL,6,FBlast Furnace 5 (BF5) has been
OL,7,Foperating since May 1959, but will
OL,8,Fshut as part of Tata Steel UK's
OL,9,Frestructure.
OL,11,FIt produced 11,800 tonnes a week,
OL,12,Fpeaking in 2009 when it was producing
OL,13,Fmore than 57,000 tonnes a week.
OL,15,FTragedy struck back in November 2001
OL,16,Fwhen an explosion in BF5 killed three
OL,17,Fsteelworkers and seriously injured 12
OL,18,Fothers.
