OL,6,FAndrew Hutin, 20, and Stephen
OL,7,FGalsworthy, 25, were killed, along
OL,8,Fwith 53-year-old Len Radford.
OL,10,FIn 2008, the Health and Safety
OL,11,FExecutive published a report on the
OL,12,Fexplosion, which blamed water entering
OL,13,Fthe blast furnace as the cause of the
OL,14,Fdisaster, following the failure of
OL,15,Fsafety-critical water cooling systems.
OL,17,FBlast Furnace 4 (BF4) is due to shut
OL,18,Fat the end of September.
