OL,6,FTata Steel plans to replace the two
OL,7,Fblast furnaces ` which produce molten
OL,8,Firon from iron ore ` with electric arc
OL,9,Ffurnaces.
OL,11,FThe company plans to place orders for
OL,12,Fthe furnace equipment by September and
OL,13,Fbegin construction by August 2025.
